@startuml
title Proxy inteligente - conteo de uso
left to right direction
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam roundcorner 8
skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0
skinparam class {
  BackgroundColor #F8FAFC
  BorderColor #334155
  ArrowColor #334155
  FontColor #0F172A
}
hide empty members

package "main" #EEF2FF {
  class Main <<cliente>>
}

package "pattern" #ECFDF5 {
  interface SharedResource <<Subject>> {
+use(client: String): void
  }
  class ExpensiveResource <<RealSubject>>
  class SmartReferenceProxy <<Proxy>>
}

SharedResource <|.. ExpensiveResource
SharedResource <|.. SmartReferenceProxy
SmartReferenceProxy --> ExpensiveResource : controla/delega
Main ..> SharedResource : usa misma interfaz

note bottom of SmartReferenceProxy
Agrega administracion alrededor del acceso: conteo, trazas o control de ciclo de vida.
end note
@enduml
